com.siperian.sif.message.metadata

Class MetaDataHmEntityType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.metadata.MetaDataBase
      • com.siperian.sif.message.metadata.MetaDataHmTypeBase
        • com.siperian.sif.message.metadata.MetaDataHmEntityType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable

    public class MetaDataHmEntityType
extends MetaDataHmTypeBase
    Represents an HM entity type. HM entity types determine what types of entities are available for use on an HM graph. Entities are connected by relationships to show how entities are related.
    See Also:
    MetaDataHmRelationshipType, DescribeSiperianObjectRequest, Serialized Form

    API Group: Metadata

      • isEntityTypeRowid

        public boolean isEntityTypeRowid()
        Determine whether the entity type column in the base object representing this entity is a rowid column.
        Returns:
        true if the entity type column in the entity base object contains the entity type's rowid, false if entity type column in the entity base object contains the entity type's name.
